Text:
Shit!! I screwed up. The files should read 2012.03.15, but instead, I accidentally typed 2013.03.15.

2011...2012...2013..its all a blur to me. They go by so fast now.
You know what...This probably isn't the first time I dated files incorrectly. I'm pretty sure I've done it before. Only this time I noticed it.
JUST A REMINDER. DO NOT CORRECT THE FILES' DATE UNTIL YOU ARE COMPLETELY FINISHED SEEDING. IT'LL MESS UP THE TORRENT.
